dct_title_s: The Solomon, New Hebrides, and Santa Cruz Groups (South Pacific Ocean) : to illustrate the paper by Lieut. A. H. Markham R.N.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Depths shown by isolines. Routes of Spanish, French, and English voyages between 1568 and 1871 are shown. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 42, (1872), pp. 213-43; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v.42 1872
dct_publisher_sm: London: published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society by J. Murray, Albemarle Strt., 1872.
